5:["$","div",null,{"className":"flex min-h-screen flex-col","children":[["$","$Le",null,{}],["$","main",null,{"className":"flex-1","children":["$","article",null,{"className":"container max-w-4xl py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"text-center space-y-4","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"font-headline text-4xl font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-5xl","children":"The Ultimate Spring 2026 Seller's Checklist: River Oaks, West Oak Trails & Palermo West"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted-foreground","children":"December 28, 2025"}]]}],["$","$Lf",null,{"className":"my-8"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none dark:prose-invert","children":[["$","h2","h2-0",{"children":"A Specialized Guide for Townhouse & Semi-Detached Homeowners"}],"\n",["$","p","p-0",{"children":"Are you thinking of selling your semi-detached home or townhouse in River Oaks, West Oak Trails, or Palermo West in the spring of 2026? This is the checklist for you. Selling in these specific, family-friendly Oakville neighbourhoods requires a tailored approach to attract the right buyers and achieve a premium price."}],"\n",["$","p","p-1",{"children":"This guide will walk you through the entire process, from planning today to a successful closing next spring."}],"\n",["$","p","p-2",{"children":["$","img","img-0",{"src":"/spring-2026-checklist.png","alt":"Spring 2026 Seller's Checklist Infographic"}]}],"\n",["$","h3","h3-0",{"children":"Phase 1: Autumn/Winter 2025 - The Strategic Planning Stage"}],"\n",["$","p","p-3",{"children":"With a Spring 2026 sale in mind, now is the perfect time to lay the groundwork."}],"\n",["$","ul","ul-0",{"className":"contains-task-list","children":["\n",["$","li","li-0",{"className":"task-list-item list-none relative pl-8 my-2","children":[["$","svg","input-0",{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 text-green-600 absolute left-0 top-1.5","children":[["$","circle","1mglay",{"cx":"12","cy":"12","r":"10"}],["$","path","dzmm74",{"d":"m9 12 2 2 4-4"}],"$undefined"]}]," ",["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Understand Your Hyper-Local Market:"}]," Don't just look at \"Oakville.\" Research the specific sale prices of comparable townhouses and semi-detached homes that have sold in your neighbourhood in the last 60 days. An expert can help you analyze how factors like end-units, finished basements, or proximity to top schools like St. Joan of Arc or West Oak Trails Public School impacted final sale prices."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-1",{"className":"task-list-item list-none relative pl-8 my-2","children":[["$","svg","input-0",{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 text-green-600 absolute left-0 top-1.5","children":[["$","circle","1mglay",{"cx":"12","cy":"12","r":"10"}],["$","path","dzmm74",{"d":"m9 12 2 2 4-4"}],"$undefined"]}]," ",["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Get a Pinpoint-Accurate Home Valuation:"}]," For townhouses and semis, value is heavily influenced by immediate neighbours. A professional valuation will compare your home's specific upgrades, layout, and condition to the most recent sales on your street and in your complex."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-2",{"className":"task-list-item list-none relative pl-8 my-2","children":[["$","svg","input-0",{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 text-green-600 absolute left-0 top-1.5","children":[["$","circle","1mglay",{"cx":"12","cy":"12","r":"10"}],"$L10","$undefined"]}]," ","$L11"," Understand your mortgage portability options and get pre-approved for your next purchase. Knowing your budget is critical before you start looking for your next home."]}],"\n","$L12","\n","$L13","\n","$L14","\n"]}],"\n","$L15","\n","$L16","\n","$L17","\n","$L18","\n","$L19","\n","$L1a","\n","$L1b","\n","$L1c","\n","$L1d"]}],"$L1e","$L1f"]}]}],"$L20","$L21"]}]
