17:["$","ul","ul-1",{"className":"contains-task-list","children":["\n",["$","li","li-0",{"className":"task-list-item list-none relative pl-8 my-2","children":[["$","svg","input-0",{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 text-green-600 absolute left-0 top-1.5","children":[["$","circle","1mglay",{"cx":"12","cy":"12","r":"10"}],["$","path","dzmm74",{"d":"m9 12 2 2 4-4"}],"$undefined"]}]," ",["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Declutter to Maximize Space:"}]," This is the #1 task for townhouses and semis. Every square foot counts. The goal is to make each room feel as large, bright, and airy as possible. Be ruthless with closets, storage areas, and the garage."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-1",{"className":"task-list-item list-none relative pl-8 my-2","children":[["$","svg","input-0",{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 text-green-600 absolute left-0 top-1.5","children":[["$","circle","1mglay",{"cx":"12","cy":"12","r":"10"}],["$","path","dzmm74",{"d":"m9 12 2 2 4-4"}],"$undefined"]}]," ",["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Depersonalize Your Space:"}]," Pack away personal items so buyers can envision their own family's life in the home. This helps create an emotional connection to the property itself."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-2",{"className":"task-list-item list-none relative pl-8 my-2","children":[["$","svg","input-0",{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 text-green-600 absolute left-0 top-1.5","children":[["$","circle","1mglay",{"cx":"12","cy":"12","r":"10"}],["$","path","dzmm74",{"d":"m9 12 2 2 4-4"}],"$undefined"]}]," ",["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Complete High-ROI Minor Repairs:"}],"\n",["$","ul","ul-0",{"children":["\n",["$","li","li-0",{"className":"$undefined","children":"Patch any scuffs on walls, especially in high-traffic hallways and staircases. A fresh coat of neutral paint is your best investment."}],"\n",["$","li","li-1",{"className":"$undefined","children":"Ensure all doors, windows, and kitchen cabinet hardware are in perfect working order."}],"\n",["$","li","li-2",{"className":"$undefined","children":"Consider updating light fixtures for a modern touch."}],"\n"]}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","li","li-3",{"className":"task-list-item list-none relative pl-8 my-2","children":[["$","svg","input-0",{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 text-green-600 absolute left-0 top-1.5","children":[["$","circle","1mglay",{"cx":"12","cy":"12","r":"10"}],["$","path","dzmm74",{"d":"m9 12 2 2 4-4"}],"$undefined"]}]," ",["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Professional-Level Deep Clean:"}]," Focus on making the entire home sparkle. Pay special attention to kitchens, bathrooms, windows, and floors."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-4",{"className":"task-list-item list-none relative pl-8 my-2","children":[["$","svg","input-0",{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-circle-check h-5 w-5 text-green-600 absolute left-0 top-1.5","children":[["$","circle","1mglay",{"cx":"12","cy":"12","r":"10"}],["$","path","dzmm74",{"d":"m9 12 2 2 4-4"}],"$undefined"]}]," ",["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Consult a Professional Stager:"}]," A stager who understands the target buyer for these neighbourhoods—often young families or professional couples—can optimize furniture layout to showcase the home's flow and functionality."]}],"\n","$L22","\n"]}]
